title: Manveer Gurjar And This Ex Bigg Boss Contestant Were Spotted Having A Dinner Date
text:
facebook 229 SHARES 
Bigg Boss season 10 winner, Manveer Gurjar, has managed to stay in the news long after he took home the trophy. Between allegations about his wedding, his arrest, and hanging out with contestant, Nitibha Kaul, he's managed to stir up quite some controversies. 
The latest news is that he was seen having a date with none other than Bigg Boss 7 contestant, Kamya Punjabi. The two recently caught up for dinner, and shared the pictures on social media. 
Take a look.
